    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Larger even than a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/weapons/weapon-descriptions/longbow\">longbow</a>, these bows are often made from the horns of great beasts. Though they have a shorter range than other bows, their greater destructive power is highly favored by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/humanoids/orc\">orcs</a>&nbsp;and their kin.</em></p>\n<p>All hornbows are composite bows and can be modified to benefit from high&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Strength-Str-\">Strength</a>&nbsp;scores in the same way as other composite bows. Any effect that applies to both longbows and shortbows also applies to hornbows.</p>",
